main event: On July 4, 1966, two witnesses observed two objects in the sky over Houston, Texas, which they initially thought could be jets due to the noise they made.
interesting points: The observer noted that the objects made a noise similar to jets or rockets., Investigating officials linked the sighting to an F-102 low level fly-by by the 147 Fighter Group, Air National Guard., The observation lasted about 1 minute., The objects were seen moving consistently without erratic motion., There were multiple reports of UFO sightings in the same region during this time period.
sighted object: Two objects making noise like jets
